{
  "texts": [
    "Keerthana et al.",
    "[24] introduced two innovative CNN hybrid approaches using an SVM classifier at the final layer for categorizing dermoscopy images into benign or melanoma tumors.",
    "The characteristics taken by the first and second CNN models were combined and passed to the SVM classifier.",
    "Using the ISBI 2016 dataset, their models obtained an accuracy of 88.02% and 87.43%.",
    "[25] uses the HAM10000 dataset to analyze the performance of EfficientNets B0-B7 models."
  ]
}